{"type": "article", "id": 35386, "title": "想看第五大道的圣诞橱窗？Google做了个项目让你身临其境", "description": "橱窗装饰的线上博物馆", "date": "2016-12-09T10:05:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1097, "name": "百货"}, {"id": 19145, "name": "第五大道"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 343708, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161208151541XlijH0wyZ32KQCbx.png", "contents": "<p>去不了纽约却对每年的第五大道圣诞橱窗好奇，想仔细看几眼？Google 做了第五大道圣诞橱窗的 VR 项目：<a href=\"https://windowwonderland.withgoogle.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">橱窗奇妙乐园（Window Wonderland）</a>也许能满足你。</p><p>Google Shopping （产品搜索和导购）和以及 Google 旗下的 Art, Copy &amp; Code 项目联合为第五大道上 18 家商店，包括百货商店梅西、Bloomingdale、Lord &amp; Taylor 和品牌零售店如 Tiffany、Burberry、卡地亚和 Micheal Kors 等拍了上百张高清图片，以达到“全景式”的逼真效果。点开小窗，你还可以在线购买橱窗里展览的商品。如下面视频所示：</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMTg1NDY1MTc0OA==\" frameborder=\"0\" 'allowfullscreen'=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>想更身临其境一点，还可以通过 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/8635.html\">Google Cardboard （纸糊的 VR 眼镜）</a>或者 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32936.html\">Google Daydrem View</a> （10 月发布的 VR 头盔，需要搭配 Pixel 手机）查看。没有设备也没关系，你还是能看到橱窗长什么样的。</p><p>它有点类似线上博物馆，可以让用户放大缩小浏览，还能听到各家店铺创意总监的解说——他们是怎样设计和布置橱窗的。<br></p><p>这是第五大道的圣诞橱窗第一次上线。Google 旗下 Art, Copy  &amp; Code 项目负责人 Aman Govil 说：“布置节日橱窗需要技艺和时间，我们希望能让世界其他地方的人也能观赏到它。”从中你看能看出 Google 普及虚拟现实内容（卖自己 VR 硬件产品）的野心；当然，它同时记录也普及了艺术。去年 Google 也做了个类似的项目：<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19551.html\">圣诞游白宫</a>。<br> </p><p>纽约百货和零售店的圣诞橱窗已经有 150 多年的历史了，而第五大道是游客和时尚人士在纽约的必经之地，说它是世界上最好看的圣诞橱窗也不为过。每年，百货商店和零售品牌还会为圣诞橱窗举办揭幕仪式。我们挑了一些好看的橱窗，你可以看看。</p><p class=\"\">梅西百货（Macy’s）的橱窗是由设计师 Roya Sullivan 创造的。 6 个橱窗据说有 <a href=\"http://www.visitmacysusa.com/blog/herald-square-holiday-windows\" rel=\"nofollow\">250 个工作人员参与，筹备了将近一年</a>。里面还有一个叫“圣诞老人的指挥中心”（Santa's command center ）的弹珠游戏。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208154638HmniuyMrTPOEozW6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500415\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208154639rYRj86H9Cd0wGupe.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.497143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081546400gfxZrkOPhwcMRKm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.489431\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208154640Oi1P2nUbFafYuL4s.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504626\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">百货商店 Lord &amp; Taylor's 的主题是魔幻森林（Enchanted Forest），找人手雕了 34 个动物雕像。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081525040nNJSVDQXtcs7edw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693431\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208152504I4xi0YkXj6BDa2bc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608410\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208152504RGhrLVKxT6Nl2A5i.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654255\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Barneys 百货的橱窗没有直接用太多圣诞元素，他们启用的主题是“爱、和平和喜悦”（Love, Peace and Joy），把不同橱窗交给了不同的艺术家和工作室（其中还包括动画《南方公园》的创始人之一 Matt Stone）。据说如果你拍照上传 Twitter，并使用“#Love, Peace and Joy”的标签，他们就会捐 5 美元给慈善机构。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208165335WP3pDAXUk2hgd7la.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521376\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208165335EMJZY7qL8lQaOs90.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628541\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208165337jfePkz8AHu9hoisb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614359\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208165337GlAkUD1sSMovdLr0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627883\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Tiffany 的橱窗主题是“让世界亮晶晶”（Make the World Sparkle）。不知道是否受到业绩不好的影响，它们今年取消了橱窗揭幕仪式（本来还请了影后&nbsp;Reese Witherspoon 来参加）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164447MHebj187XoRGiJLl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653499\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081644485Bd7yQYPu4t6RGOf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683010\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164448XSQeO0kDTLmiufMW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654977\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164448SZEiohds9G01QHxv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640642\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">百货商店 Bloomingdale 找了 8 位艺术家根据“光”这一命题做了 8 个作品，圣诞结束后这些装置将被拍卖，收入将捐给慈善机构 Child Mind Institute。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164921kh43JeOpMmx72oLf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.922958\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164922XsEVzqvd9GFTly13.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.867176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164922OKt0HTLj5srPx4u1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.940058\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164922mQn8Kp2eVkREHBto.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.894030\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164923q782IZwYSpUKXk1o.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.914504\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164923IepdgqrBS8PF9RyH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.898051\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164925sRHIi0CQ6ZY95D4n.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.890093\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164925XASf52NkxQCwg1Mc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.910765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Saks Fifth Avenue 为圣诞橱窗做了揭幕仪式。它今年的主题是“千盏灯的光明之地”（Land of 1000 lights），用到了很多糖果的元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164041XQpWOKZSvw2dxEIg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796853\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164042jIwJahfmoBYrH2Zz.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.847662\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164042tMeSx62913YzhvuA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.591897\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164043KpAuvqOaCDxnSlNZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.852632\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081640437kvoxzA3WtUSFyrc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687281\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208164044WIAjUbgsMNOy7ZFR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.835148\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">图片来自 Google 或视频截图</p>"}